title: Slowdive - Pygmalion Demos And More
description:
Another collection of demos following on from the I Saw The Sun compilation.

Details:-

Tracks 1 and 2 are from a 7" flexi single
Tracks 3 and 4 are demos from the Souvlaki sessions which werent included on the I Saw The Sun compilation.
Track 5 is remix of shine
Tracks 6 to 17 are all Pygmalion demos from 1994.

Bitrate is a bit mixed as tracks have come from various sources but sound is generally ok.

Comments or further information welcome. Enjoy and Please Seed....
